text:
20 years.....
For someone in 2005, days passed without much changing
Looking back however, it only took us 20 years to get from low quality 144p videos to 8k on a device that can fit into our pockets.
How just 2 years back, AI would generate a mix of sharks and snakes into scary monsters with the animals having 3-4 or no eyes, limbs, no mouths, etc. to being able to modify existing images seamlessly.

I am very happy this video still exists, like a digital statue, holding memories, milestones and serving as a reminder of humanity's growth as a whole....
